saying to cheer up someone when something bad happens, and to tell them that maybe something

8
00:00:39,820 --> 00:00:44,940
good comes out of something bad. Let's take a look at what this is, and also what it's not.

9
00:00:45,740 --> 00:00:50,940
Let's motivate this with an example. Say you have a friend named Steve. He started his own company,

10
