through a really difficult situation. In psychology, this is called toxic positivity in that it's

26
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:20,720
attempting to get someone to think positive without first acknowledging the real negatives

27
00:02:21,160 --> 00:02:25,620
that they're going through. So there's a fine line. When you say every cloud has a silver lining,

28
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:31,180
